Usage: cycledit <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list      List files with their last-modified date
  schedule  Show the full edit schedule
  now       Show only files due now (`chunk_date <= today`)
  check     Check if any files are due; exits 100 if so
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
